’Щ@117648c3225452337ef8a2cc34027615d60d7514705fc46d8e67d060381f8ed3Ъ)Title: title: bytes reverse
Path: Examples
Content:
Reverse bytes 
``0x[1F FF AA AA]``
.
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> 0x[1F FF AA AA] | bytes reverse
Length: 4 (0x4) bytes | null_char printable whitespace ascii_other non_ascii
00000000:   aa aa ff 1f                                          Г—Г—Г—вЂў


```
Reverse bytes 
``0x[FF AA AA]``
.
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> 0x[FF AA AA] | bytes reverse
Length: 3 (0x3) bytes | null_char printable whitespace ascii_other non_ascii
00000000:   aa aa ff                                             Г—Г—Г—


```
